{"tid":1846720,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"FCed - 康文署設施明日起暫停開放","createTime":"2020-01-27T17:13:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T17:20:28.000Z","uid":193167,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"df9811504fbc59ccf9a096be7356dd32b05451da","tid":1846720,"uid":193167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:13:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202001/28/P2020012800027.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202001%2F28%2FP2020012800027.htm&d=gjA94EiKSJsk9JMrtOnM5o6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=05b495d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202001/28/P2020012800027.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n康文署設施明日起暫停開放<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n　　康樂及文化事務署今日（一月二十八日）宣布，為配合政府「對公共衞生有重要性的新型傳染病預備及應變計劃」下提升應變級別至緊急及避免市民聚集，以下文康設施將由明日（一月二十九日）起暫停開放，並取消在有關場地舉行的康樂、體育及文化活動，直至另行通告。<br />\n<br />\n　　暫停開放的陸上和水上運動設施包括所有體育館、運動場、草地球場、人造草地足球場、網球場、壁球場、草地滾球場、高爾夫球設施、公眾游泳池、泳灘、屯門康樂體育中心、水上活動中心和度假營。文化設施則包括所有博物館、表演場地、公共圖書館及附設之自修室、流動圖書館，以及音樂事務處的音樂中心。<br />\n<br />\n　　有關退票／款安排署方將稍後公布。<br />\n　　 <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年1月28日（星期二）<br />\n香港時間0時46分"},{"pid":"4bf381e324753b19da9f9ad5f7e421730ddfbf61","tid":1846720,"uid":205552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:16:35.000Z","msg":"代表好撚大鑊"},{"pid":"75efad9c403dbed246d216cea67564206ea097bf","tid":1846720,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:17:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">除咗醫護之外<br />\n垃圾政府都推緊社福界去死</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要求立即停止所有非緊急服務</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845195\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845195</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AS4YPwC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAS4YPwC.jpg&h=a350fa60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"29a9a27c52cd62e8b4c8a8333ecd849112166707","tid":1846720,"uid":120249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:17:55.000Z","msg":"室外果啲都唔開？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a8c093e0ed610c045da6598bfcd870e295e285","tid":1846720,"uid":39226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:18:46.000Z","msg":"室外個啲跑步運動場都唔開？"},{"pid":"6451fd290cf8d809e82219d15410fd1285fecce9","tid":1846720,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74a8c093e0ed610c045da6598bfcd870e295e285","tid":1846720,"uid":39226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:18:46.000Z","msg":"室外個啲跑步運動場都唔開？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:20:28.000Z","msg":"呢啲應該係屬於運動場嘅類別"}]}